Rules:
- Personality must use Big Five format with scores 1-10
- biography MUST be included for every NPC — this is critical for immersion. Make each biography unique, specific, and personal. No generic backgrounds.
- Level range: 1-15 based on description (most villagers are 1-3, veterans 5-8, powerful figures 10+)
- HP = class hit die average × level (fighter d10, rogue d8, wizard d6, cleric d8)
- AC = 10 + dex_mod + armor (if any)
- ability_scores should reflect their occupation and personality
- Assign relationships between characters where implied
